<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{description}}" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f4f4f5;
        --paper: #ffffff;
        --ink: #101828;
        --muted: #475467;
        --line: #eaecf0;
        --line-strong: #d0d5dd;
        --accent: #0b4a6f;
        --accent-strong: #083a57;
        --success: #027a48;
        --panel: #f9fafb;
        --code: #101828;
        --code-border: #1d2939;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(11, 74, 111, 0.14), transparent 24%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #eef2f6 0%, var(--bg) 280px, var(--bg) 100%);
      }
      a { color: var(--accent); }
      .wrap {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 24px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px 0 56px;
      }
      .shell {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 280px minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 24px;
        align-items: start;
      }
      .nav {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }
      .sidebar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 24px;
      }
      .sidebar-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 18px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.05);
      }
      .brand {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      }
      .brand-mark {
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #101828 0%, #0b4a6f 100%);
        color: #fff;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font: 800 0.95rem/1 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(11, 74, 111, 0.22);
      }
      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }
      .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        font: 600 0.92rem/1.2 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 11px 13px;
      }
      .nav-links a:hover {
        border-color: var(--line-strong);
        background: #fff;
      }
      .hero {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background:
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), transparent 45%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #101828 0%, #0f1723 100%);
        border: 1px solid #1d2939;
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 32px;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 48px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.16);
      }
      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font: 700 12px/1.2 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #98a2b3;
      }
      .eyebrow::before {
        content: "";
        width: 28px;
        height: 1px;
        background: #667085;
      }
      h1, h2, h3 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.9rem);
        max-width: 11ch;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }
      h2 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); margin-top: 28px; }
      h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--ink); }
      p, li {
        font: 400 1rem/1.65 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .hero-grid,
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
      }
      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
        align-items: start;
      }
      .hero-copy p {
        color: #cfd4dc;
        max-width: 62ch;
        font-size: 1.02rem;
      }
      .hero-stats {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 22px;
      }
      .hero-stat {
        min-width: 150px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }
      .hero-stat strong {
        display: block;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
      .hero-stat span {
        color: #98a2b3;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .links,
      .card,
      .endpoint,
      .snippet {
        background: var(--paper);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
      .links,
      .card,
      .endpoint,
      .snippet {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .links {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
      }
      .link-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }
      .link-pill {
        display: block;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: #f2f4f7;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        text-decoration: none;
        font: 600 0.96rem/1.3 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .section {
        margin-top: 32px;
      }
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
      .endpoint-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #ecfdf3;
        color: var(--success);
        font: 700 0.76rem/1 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .path {
        margin-top: 10px;
        font: 700 1rem/1.4 ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
        word-break: break-word;
      }
      .meta {
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        font: 600 0.9rem/1.4 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
      }
      .card,
      .endpoint,
      .snippet {
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04);
      }
      .endpoint-head {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .endpoint-auth {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 7px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--muted);
        font: 600 0.82rem/1 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .endpoint-body {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 0.95fr);
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 12px;
        align-items: start;
      }
      .endpoint-copy p {
        margin: 0;
      }
      .endpoint-copy ul {
        margin-top: 12px;
      }
      .endpoint-examples {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
      }
      .example-block h3 {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 0.96rem;
      }
      pre {
        margin: 12px 0 0;
        padding: 16px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 100%;
        overflow-x: auto;
        overflow-y: hidden;
        white-space: pre;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: var(--code);
        border: 1px solid var(--code-border);
        color: #f5f7f7;
        font: 0.88rem/1.55 ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      }
      .endpoint,
      .snippet,
      .example-block {
        min-width: 0;
      }
      .endpoint-examples,
      .example-block {
        min-width: 0;
      }
      code {
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      }
      .inline-code {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 2px 8px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #f2f4f7;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        color: var(--ink);
        font-size: 0.92em;
      }
      ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin: 10px 0 0;
      }
      .mini {
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }
      .callout {
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: #f2f4f7;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
      }
      .callout strong {
        color: var(--ink);
      }
      .section-kicker {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font: 700 0.8rem/1 "Inter", "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .sidebar-note {
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding-top: 18px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      }
      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .shell {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .sidebar {
          position: static;
        }
        .nav {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .hero-grid,
        .grid,
        .endpoint-grid,
        .endpoint-body {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .wrap {
          width: min(100% - 16px, 1120px);
        }
        .hero {
          padding: 24px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <div class="shell">
        <aside class="sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <div class="brand">
              <span class="brand-mark">M</span>
              <span>MyTrackr for Developers</span>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-links">
              <a href="#flow">Flow</a>
              <a href="#setup-endpoints">Setup</a>
              <a href="#runtime-endpoints">Runtime</a>
              <a href="#webhook-receiver">Webhooks</a>
              <a href="#code-examples">Examples</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-note">
              <h3>Quick Access</h3>
              <div class="link-list">
                <a class="link-pill" href="{{swaggerUrl}}">Open Swagger UI</a>
                <a class="link-pill" href="{{swaggerJsonUrl}}">Open Swagger JSON</a>
              </div>
              <p class="mini">
                Base URL: <span class="inline-code">{{baseUrl}}</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <div>
          <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-grid">
              <div class="hero-copy">
                <div class="eyebrow">Developer Guide</div>
                <h1>{{title}}</h1>
                <p>
                  Connect storefronts, push ecommerce events, and expose clean financial visibility inside MyTrackr.
                  This guide covers the current production flow: integrations are enabled by the app subscription, not by a separate checkout.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-stats">
                  <div class="hero-stat">
                    <strong>Web or Unlimited</strong>
                    <span>Required subscription</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="hero-stat">
                    <strong>Server-to-server</strong>
                    <span>Primary integration model</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="hero-stat">
                    <strong>/swagger-json</strong>
                    <span>Machine-readable reference</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <aside class="links">
                <h3>Start Here</h3>
                <p class="mini">
                  Create the integration while logged into the app, then keep the returned
                  <span class="inline-code">apiKey</span> on your server.
                </p>
                <div class="callout">
                  <strong>Important:</strong> browser-facing code should use the public config endpoint. Private config, event ingestion, metrics, and Paystack sync belong on your backend.
                </div>
              </aside>
            </div>
          </section>

      <section class="section" id="flow">
        <span class="section-kicker">Overview</span>
        <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Access rules</h3>
            <ul>
              {{#each prerequisites}}
              <li>{{this}}</li>
              {{/each}}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Supported event types</h3>
            <ul>
              {{#each eventTypes}}
              <li><code>{{this}}</code></li>
              {{/each}}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <span class="section-kicker">Guide</span>
        <h2>Integration Flow</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          {{#each steps}}
          <article class="card">
            <h3>{{title}}</h3>
            <p>{{body}}</p>
          </article>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </section>

      {{#each endpointGroups}}
      <section class="section" id="{{id}}">
        <span class="section-kicker">Reference</span>
        <h2>{{title}} Endpoints</h2>
        <div class="endpoint-grid">
          {{#each endpoints}}
          <article class="endpoint">
            <div class="endpoint-head">
              <div>
                <span class="badge">{{method}}</span>
                <div class="path">{{path}}</div>
              </div>
              <span class="endpoint-auth">Auth: {{auth}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="endpoint-body">
              <div class="endpoint-copy">
                <p>{{summary}}</p>
                {{#if notes}}
                <ul>
                  {{#each notes}}
                  <li>{{this}}</li>
                  {{/each}}
                </ul>
                {{/if}}
              </div>
              <div class="endpoint-examples">
                {{#if requestExample}}
                <div class="example-block">
                  <h3>Request</h3>
                  <pre><code>{{requestExample}}</code></pre>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if responseExample}}
                <div class="example-block">
                  <h3>Response</h3>
                  <pre><code>{{responseExample}}</code></pre>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </section>
      {{/each}}

      <section class="section" id="webhook-receiver">
        <span class="section-kicker">Delivery</span>
        <h2>Webhook Receiver</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>When MyTrackr calls your webhookUrl</h3>
            <p>
              If an integration has a <span class="inline-code">webhookUrl</span>, MyTrackr sends outbound POST webhooks for lifecycle,
              event-ingestion, and Paystack sync updates.
            </p>
            <ul>
              {{#each webhookEvents}}
              <li><code>{{this}}</code></li>
              {{/each}}
            </ul>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Headers</h3>
            <ul>
              {{#each webhookHeaders}}
              <li><span class="inline-code">{{name}}</span>: {{description}}</li>
              {{/each}}
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
          <article class="snippet">
            <h3>Webhook Envelope</h3>
            <pre><code>{{webhookPayloadExample}}</code></pre>
          </article>
          <article class="snippet">
            <h3>Another Event Example</h3>
            <pre><code>{{webhookVerificationExample}}</code></pre>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="callout">
          <strong>Signature verification:</strong> compute an HMAC-SHA256 of the raw request body using
          <span class="inline-code">INTEGRATION_WEBHOOK_SECRET</span> and compare it with
          <span class="inline-code">x-mytrackr-signature</span>.
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="code-examples">
        <span class="section-kicker">Implementation</span>
        <h2>Code Examples</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          {{#each codeExamples}}
          <article class="snippet">
            <h3>{{title}}</h3>
            <p class="mini">Language: <code>{{language}}</code></p>
            <pre><code>{{code}}</code></pre>
          </article>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
